data.description: !! FULLY REMODELED DREAM HOME !! MOVE IN READY !! Three bedrooms + two bathrooms + 2 car garage in Yukon with Piedmont Schools. Fully remodeled by current owners: dark tile flooring throughout, new interior paint, open concept, completely remodeled kitchen, walk in pantry, walk in closet in master bedroom, newly remodeled master bathroom with his and her sinks and a beautiful walk-in shower with clear white tile. Floor plan is open living, dining, and kitchen with two bedrooms and a remodeled hallway bathroom, master bedroom and mater bathroom. A very large backyard with a covered porch, fireplace, and grill - perfect for cooking outside and entertaining. Location near NW Expressway and Council Rd within driving distance of the turnpike plus so many restaurants, groceries and shopping nearby. Roof replacement completed August 2023.
